727020f-a.title: Queens: Jamaica Avenue - 134th Street
727020f-a.text:
Jamaica Avenue, east from 134th Street, showing the un-
developed plots on the north side of the avenue, seen from
underneath the B.M.T. subway structure. The houses across the
auto parking space are on Metropolitan Avenue. The latter, ss
well as Kew Gardens Road, join Jamaica Avenue just beyond the
diner (center right).
P. L. Sperr  May 7, 1934
NO REPRODUCTIONS
